Uses of Package
gs.spri.raven.core

  • Packages that use gs.spri.raven.core 
    Package Description
    gs.spri.raven
    High level classes to make use of the raven authentication service.
    gs.spri.raven.core
    Low level classes representing the authentication process, the request to raven and the token it returns.
  • Classes in gs.spri.raven.core used by gs.spri.raven 
    Class and Description
    RavenException
    An Exception thrown by RavenAuthenticator to indicate unsuccessful authentication.
    RavenStateException
    A RavenException that is thrown because Raven found itself at the wrong point in its state machine.
    Request
    Encapsulates all of the data sent to Raven in an Authentication Request.
    Token
    Represents authentication data received from Raven.
